name: Yogyakarta Dare to Challenge
description:
The best outdoor trip for outdoor freaks!
We provide you off-road vehicles and take you to the 3rd grade rafting on Elo river, also enjoy the traditional meals from an amazing cultural village near the Borobudur temple. Keep your faith and enjoy the view while some ropes deliver us into the Jomblang vertical cave, get your finger ready for rock climbing at Siung Beach International Rock Climbing Area.
Take your time for body rafting and cave tubing at Bejiharjo village, the best caves compound in town.
